| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7130 — Recovery Inhibition (threeam)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: aea2047f-86ff-5ce5-8fea-3a1737a7a3f8"
